title: "Putting it all together" - a secure deployment ready NodeJs crud app
description: I will demonstrate how to build and end to end NodeJS webapp including authentication, client side validation, and logging. I will be using the following technologies for the discussion and demonstration: Nodejs, Express, PassportJS, Mongoose, Angular, and Bootstrap. photoAlt: Matthew Phillips JavaScript developer Louisville, KY December 16, 2015
title: Build the fastest single page applications with DoneJS
description: Learn how to build the fastest single page applications with DoneJS (donejs.com). This talk details some most important performance techniques used in single page applications like: server side rendering, progressively loading optimized bundles, and use of content delivery networks. We will discover how DoneJS solves these problems while building a simple real-time chat application.

photoAlt: Clayton Hunt JavaScript developer Louisville, KY October 21, 2015
title: Making 'this' Go Away
